column5: Hi, Can anyone give me the names/phone numbers for duty free shops in International Falls...thanks.

Can not help you with a name or phone number, but, there is a duty free shop on the left side of the street just before you reach the bridge going into Fort Francis. A big duty free sign next to it so you can't miss it. Opens at 8am and has good selection of alcohol, cigarettes. The pickup point is a liittle shed just as you start onto the bridge.
Thanks for the info. I seem to recall a "BORDER BOB'S" or something like that...can't remember for sure.If anyone has a name or phone number I'd appreciate it...thanks again

There is an AMEX exchange place in the location mentioned. Looks like it was a gas station at one time. AMEX has specials on brew once in a while (buy five cases of Blue for the price of four etc). Remember you must declare that duty free beer! I believe Border Bob's is in the next building.
